# Surelyy AI

AI powered recommendation engine for products, movies, and tools.

## Live Demo

[Visit Surelyy](https://your-surelyy-url.com)

## Overview

Surelyy generates personalized recommendations based on user preferences.  
It processes structured inputs, applies filtering logic, ranks results, and returns optimized suggestions.

## Features

- Personalized recommendation flow  
- Preference based filtering  
- Dynamic ranking logic  
- Clean UI for input and output  


## How It Works

1. User submits preferences.  
2. System validates and structures input data.  
3. Filtering engine narrows candidate results.  
4. Ranking logic scores and sorts outputs.  
5. Top results are returned to the user.


